    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>A: &ldquo;I have to survive here for a week?&rdquo;</li>
<li>B: &ldquo;Anyone who can survive in New York can survive here.&rdquo;</li>
</ul>


<p>优秀的设计师不会默默无闻的埋没于任何一个地方，尤其这个信息时代。<br/>
平庸只能说明你还不够优秀。</p>
